code: import HttpClient from"../HttpClient";export var saveCompany=function saveCompany(model){return new Promise(function(resolve,reject){HttpClient.post('/Company/SaveCompany',model).then(function(response){resolve(response);}).catch(function(error){resolve(error.response);});});};export var getCompanyById=function getCompanyById(id){return new Promise(function(resolve,reject){HttpClient.get('/Company/GetCompanyById?companyid='+id).then(function(response){resolve(response);}).catch(function(error){resolve(error.response);});});};
